---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import ContactForm from '../../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Cibolo & Schertz Neighborhoods | Cody Posey Real Estate"
  description="Explore the top neighborhoods in Cibolo and Schertz, TX. From Saddle Creek Ranch to Verde Ranch — find the right community for your family."
>
  <Navbar />
  <main style="padding-top: 80px;">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="cs-hero">
      <div class="cs-hero__overlay"></div>
      <div class="cs-hero__content">
        <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="/cibolo-schertz/">Cibolo / Schertz</a> <span>/</span> <span>Neighborhoods</span>
        </nav>
        <h1>Cibolo / Schertz <span style="color:#FF1616;">Neighborhoods</span></h1>
        <p>Find the community that fits your family and lifestyle</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="cs-page-intro cs-page-intro--centered">The Cibolo/Schertz area offers a variety of well-established and newer neighborhoods, all served by the highly rated SCUCISD school district. Whether you're looking for a starter home or an executive property, there's a community here for you.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Neighborhoods -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--light-gray);">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Top <span class="accent">Neighborhoods</span></h2>
        </div>

        <div class="cs-hood">
          <div class="cs-hood__header">
            <h3>Saddle Creek Ranch</h3>
            <span class="cs-hood__price">$300K - $450K</span>
          </div>
          <p>One of the most popular communities in the area, Saddle Creek Ranch features a dog park, golf course, community pool, and walking trails. Homes range from traditional to Hill Country-inspired designs. Served by SCUCISD schools, this neighborhood is a top choice for families seeking an active lifestyle with resort-style amenities.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cs-hood">
          <div class="cs-hood__header">
            <h3>Falcon Ridge</h3>
            <span class="cs-hood__price">$280K - $400K</span>
          </div>
          <p>An established neighborhood near FM 1103 with mature landscaping and a strong sense of community. Falcon Ridge offers a mix of single-story and two-story homes with generous lot sizes. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and I-35 access, and served by SCUCISD schools.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cs-hood">
          <div class="cs-hood__header">
            <h3>Bentwood Ranch</h3>
            <span class="cs-hood__price">$280K - $380K</span>
          </div>
          <p>A community known for its neighborhood events and family-friendly atmosphere. Bentwood Ranch features well-maintained common areas, a community pool, and playgrounds. Homes are a mix of newer and established builds, all within the SCUCISD school district.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cs-hood">
          <div class="cs-hood__header">
            <h3>Turning Stone</h3>
            <span class="cs-hood__price">$350K - $450K</span>
          </div>
          <p>An executive-home community offering larger floor plans and premium finishes. Turning Stone is ideal for move-up buyers looking for more space and upgraded features. The neighborhood is well-kept with wide streets and mature trees, and is served by SCUCISD schools.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cs-hood">
          <div class="cs-hood__header">
            <h3>Cibolo Valley Ranch</h3>
            <span class="cs-hood__price">$250K - $350K</span>
          </div>
          <p>A newer, family-oriented community with modern home designs and community amenities. Cibolo Valley Ranch is popular with first-time buyers and young families looking for affordable options within the SCUCISD school district. The neighborhood features parks, walking paths, and a community pool.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cs-hood">
          <div class="cs-hood__header">
            <h3>Verde Ranch</h3>
            <span class="cs-hood__price">$300K - $420K</span>
          </div>
          <p>A growing community with a resort-style community pool, splash pad, and playground. Verde Ranch offers a range of floor plans from multiple builders, with homes designed for modern family living. Served by SCUCISD schools and conveniently located near retail and dining options.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- School District -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>School <span class="accent">District</span></h2>
          <p>One of the highest-rated school districts in the San Antonio metro</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-schools__grid">
          <a href="https://www.scuc.txed.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cs-schools__card">
            <h3>Schertz-Cibolo-Universal City ISD (SCUCISD)</h3>
            <p>An A-rated district known for academic excellence, strong athletics, and community engagement. Steele High School and Byron P. Steele II are among the top-rated campuses. The district serves Schertz, Cibolo, and Universal City.</p>
            <span class="cs-schools__link">Visit SCUCISD Website →</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section" style="background: #000; color: #fff; text-align: center;">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Need Help <span class="accent">Choosing a Neighborhood</span>?</h2>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); max-width: 600px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem;">I can walk you through the differences between communities and help you focus your search on neighborhoods that match your priorities.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get Help Choosing a Neighborhood</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <ContactForm context="I need help choosing a neighborhood in Cibolo/Schertz..." />
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .cs-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 280px;
    background: #000;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .cs-hero__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000 0%, #1a0000 100%);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .cs-hero__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .cs-hero__content h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .cs-hero__content p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  .breadcrumb span {
    margin: 0 0.3rem;
  }

  .cs-page-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .cs-page-intro--centered {
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--black);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Neighborhood Cards */
  .cs-hood {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .cs-hood__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cs-hood__header h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .cs-hood__price {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #FF1616;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .cs-hood p {
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Schools */
  .cs-schools__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cs-schools__card {
    display: block;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cs-schools__card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .cs-schools__card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #000;
  }

  .cs-schools__card:hover h3 {
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  .cs-schools__card p {
    color: var(--gray);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cs-schools__link {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cs-hood__header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
